      <title>Fireblocks 首席执行官谈纽约吸引人才</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/fireblocks-ceo-on-attracting-talent-in-nyc-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Michael Shaulov 是数字资产安全平台 Fireblocks 的首席执行官，该平台帮助金融机构保护数字资产免遭黑客和盗窃。他在《彭博科技》节目中与 Caroline Hyde 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/fireblocks-ceo-on-attracting-talent-in-nyc-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:33:03 GMT</pubDate>
