    <item>
      <title>纽约银行分析师 Colton Grant 表示，欧洲央行可能在 2024 年降息四次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/ecb-may-cut-four-times-in-2024-bny-s-colton-grant-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约梅隆银行财富管理首席投资官 Sinead Colton Grant 讨论了她对欧洲央行和美联储降息的预测。Colton Grant 在彭博电视上还讨论了纽约梅隆银行对家族理财室的调查结果。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/ecb-may-cut-four-times-in-2024-bny-s-colton-grant-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:32:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pacer ETFs 总裁谈美国小型股 ETF (CALF)</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/pacer-etfs-president-on-us-small-cap-etf-calf-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pacer ETFs 总裁 Sean O&#39;Hara 讨论了 Pacer US Small Cap Cash Cows 100 ETF（股票代码：CALF），该基金旨在通过筛选标准普尔 SmallCap 600 指数中自由现金流收益率较高的公司来实现资本增值。他在“Bloomberg ETF IQ”节目中与 Katie Greifeld、Scarlet Fu 和 Eric Balchunas 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/pacer-etfs-president-on-us-small-cap-etf-calf-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:27:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约科技周拉开帷幕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/new-york-tech-week-kicks-off-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约科技周已在纽约正式拉开帷幕，行业巨头和初创企业将齐聚一堂，参加活动、座谈会、对话等。Julie Samuels 是 Tech:NYC 的首席执行官，该组织代表纽约不断发展的科技行业。她在《彭博科技》节目中与 Caroline Hyde 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/new-york-tech-week-kicks-off-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国 ETF 出现大量资金流出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/china-etfs-see-major-outflows-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国 ETF 出现一年多来最大资金流出，上海和深圳 5 月份共计流出 42 亿美元。彭博社的卡罗莱纳·威尔逊 (Carolina Wilson) 报道了此事。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/china-etfs-see-major-outflows-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:01:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
